my son.

00:13.360 --> 00:15.828
- Get out of the car, now!
- Davis: What happened
that night?

00:15.880 --> 00:17.051
Micah:
He takes out his gun

00:17.100 --> 00:19.273
and he pulled
the trigger, Dad.

00:19.320 --> 00:21.402
I like you, Nova.

00:21.450 --> 00:23.315
