for the rest of my life.

00:27.670 --> 00:29.069
Will you marry me?

00:29.110 --> 00:31.670
Yes.

00:31.720 --> 00:34.803
- [ bell tolling ]
- Ralph Angel: When that girl
was like, "No, no, no, no,"

00:34.860 --> 00:36.066
that's when I knew.

00:36.120 --> 00:37.724
Darla:
What? No way.

00:37.770 --> 00:39.419
- That's when you knew?
- I mean, I felt it.

00:39.470 --> 00:41.290
- You knew it
or you felt It?
- I felt it.

00:41.340 --> 00:44.036
Your boy
was running at him
like a linebacker,

00:44.080 --> 00:45.684
and then just goes
around him.

00:45.740 --> 00:47.605
Man, that ain't real.

00:47.650 --> 00:49.868
And white daddy's
acting all smart,
that ain't real either.

00:49.910 --> 00:51.081
_Girlfriend
acting Innocent.

