them pieces together.

00:52.480 --> 00:55.085
- Yes, I did. Yeah.
- Okay, okay.

00:55.140 --> 00:57.392
Considering you haven't seen
a movie in over a year,

00:57.440 --> 00:59.783
- I will just take pleasure
inmemdm
- Cold shot.

00:59.840 --> 01:01.319
