that you liked.

01:01.360 --> 01:03.089
Yeah,
you ain't lying.

01:03.150 --> 01:04.959
You always got me watching
them weird movies

01:05.020 --> 01:06.794
with them white folks
not saying nothing.

01:06.840 --> 01:09.752
Whatever. I love
independent films, okay?

01:09.800 --> 01:12.325
I'm all for independence,
trust me.

01:12.370 --> 01:15.100
All I'm saying is
can I see some black folks
or something?

01:15.160 --> 01:16.969
[laughs]

01:17.030 --> 01:18.543
Remember we used
to go to Audubon?

01:18.600 --> 01:20.409
- Mm-hmm.
- Lay up in the park,

01:20.470 --> 01:22.370
watching ferries
float down the river?

01:22.430 --> 01:24.079
You were always wondering
where they were going.

01:24.120 --> 01:27.556
[ sighs ]
You ever miss it?

01:27.600 --> 01:31.422
- What?
- I don't know,
college life?

01:31.480 --> 01:33.948
Living in the city?
All of it?

01:35.480 --> 01:38.267
Do I wish
I'd done things
differently?

01:38.310 --> 01:39.561
Of course.

01:41.710 --> 01:43.314
I wish
I'd finished school.

01:44.450 --> 01:46.406
- [ sighs ]
- Hey.

01:46.450 --> 01:48.668
- You asked, Ralph Angel.
- I know.

01:53.110 --> 01:54.589
Whatever I wish
I'd done differently

01:54.630 --> 01:56.495
has nothing
to do with you.

01:59.110 --> 02:01.453
I think about
all the shit I've done,

02:01.510 --> 02:05.241
things I told myself
to make it make sense
in my head,

02:05.290 --> 02:07.167
knowing I was dead wrong.

02:08.430 --> 02:10.421
But once we know,
we know.

02:11.820 --> 02:13.469
Once we know, we know.

02:15.220 --> 02:17.859
Every moment

02:17.920 --> 02:19.399
You're all mine.

