Davis West

03:05.700 --> 03:09.909
and his wife,
Charley Bordelon-West,
have officially divorced.

03:09.970 --> 03:12.052
They were one of the most
powerful couples

03:12.100 --> 03:14.887
in professional sports
until their storybook romance

03:14.930 --> 03:17.182
ended in a shocking scandal.

03:17.240 --> 03:19.014
The divorce announcement
comes on the heels

03:19.060 --> 03:21.233
of a fascinating
"Gallant" magazine article

03:21.280 --> 03:24.750
detailing the former
Mrs. West's new life
as a sugar mill owner

03:24.810 --> 03:27.062
- in rural Louisiana.
- [ phone chimes ]

03:28.550 --> 03:30.541
- [ scoffing ]
- [ knocking on door ]

03:38.300 --> 03:40.689
Hey.

03:40.740 --> 03:42.776
All the world
knows now.

03:45.350 --> 03:47.739
Ifeel like I can
finally breathe again.

03:59.280 --> 04:01.145
So, what do you say?

04:01.190 --> 04:02.839
You and me tonight?

04:03.980 --> 04:06.016
Gumbo up to your elbows.

04:06.070 --> 04:07.753
And I promise you,

04:07.810 --> 04:09.539
