it'll make you holler.

04:15.080 --> 04:16.980
You wanna make me
holler, huh?

04:18.730 --> 04:21.335
[ chuckles ]

04:21.390 --> 04:25.508
I understand,
and I really appreciate
the call.

04:25.560 --> 04:27.869
Thank you.

04:27.910 --> 04:29.252
[ sighs ]

04:34.270 --> 04:36.613
Go on.

04:36.660 --> 04:38.525
It's not gonna open itself.

04:47.280 --> 04:49.453
A front-page story
should be celebrated,

04:49.500 --> 04:53.846
and I figured
flowers would be
too, you know, predictable.

04:57.550 --> 04:59.245
It's beautiful.

05:02.820 --> 05:04.856
Thank you.
[ giggles ]

05:06.820 --> 05:08.640
- Was that your editor?
- Publisher.

05:08.690 --> 05:10.646
He said the piece
is an example

05:10.700 --> 05:12.509
of what the paper
does best.

05:12.570 --> 05:14.219
[ exhales ]
It's sobering.

05:14.270 --> 05:16.522
He thought I hit
a little too close to home.

05:16.570 --> 05:18.390
Yeah.

05:18.440 --> 05:19.919
"In addition
to birth defects,

05:19.970 --> 05:21.926
researchers now believe
the ZIka Virus

