05:24.930 --> 05:27.922
An outbreak in the city's
all but forgotten Ninth Ward

05:27.970 --> 05:29.403
would have
a catastrophic effect

05:29.450 --> 05:31.327
on the state's
public health system.

05:31.370 --> 05:35.898
Experts believe it's not
a question of if, but when."

05:35.940 --> 05:39.410
I got voicemails
from city officials,
state legislators--

05:39.460 --> 05:41.678
Not one of them
has two nickels
to rub together.

05:41.730 --> 05:44.426
Zika is a hurricane
by another name.

05:44.470 --> 05:47.598
And believe me, Nova.
You connected the dots.

05:49.080 --> 05:51.685
You basically lived
on an airplane

05:51.740 --> 05:53.992
these last three weeks.

05:54.040 --> 05:58.397
The research
you've shared,
your patience...

05:58.440 --> 06:00.431
I'm so grateful, Robert.

06:02.360 --> 06:04.260
Ah...

06:04.320 --> 06:06.481
[ music playing ]

06:09.020 --> 06:11.921
I saw in the news
that Charley finally
divorced Davis.

06:11.980 --> 06:15.279
- Mm.
- Should've left his sorry ass
a long time ago.

06:15.330 --> 06:18.629
Well, you know there are
some good ones, right?

06:18.680 --> 06:20.636
Not everyone
can catch a Hollywood.

06:20.680 --> 06:22.454
[ both laughing ]

06:22.510 --> 06:25.764
You make it sound like
I went fishing, girl.

06:25.820 --> 06:27.765
I just wanna know
what you used for bait

06:27.820 --> 06:29.640
'cause I need something
on my hook.

06:29.690 --> 06:31.817
[ laughing ]

06:35.090 --> 06:39.652
You know, your hair,
it's, uh...

06:40.870 --> 06:42.394
It's falling out
a little.

06:44.440 --> 06:46.351
You going through
the change, Vi?

06:46.400 --> 06:49.221
I went through
that a while ago
at a very young age.

06:49.270 --> 06:53.309
It's, um--
you know, it's probably
a little bit of stress.

06:53.360 --> 06:55.442
You might need to get this
checked out, girl.

06:55.500 --> 06:59.322
What?
It's probably
just my wigs.

06:59.370 --> 07:01.759
You know, I need to stop
wearing them so much.

07:01.810 --> 07:04.768
Let the hair rest,
give it some fresh air,
that's all.

07:06.250 --> 07:07.638
Okay.

07:11.470 --> 07:13.779
- [ both laughing ]
- Don't laugh!

07:13.820 --> 07:17.608
I'm telling you,
I always wanted
to be a chef

07:17.650 --> 07:19.470
ever since
I was a kId.

