by your intensity.

13:53.440 --> 13:54.953
Fair enough.

13:55.000 --> 13:56.479
But don't doubt
your Integrity

13:56.530 --> 13:58.043
for a minute.

14:01.920 --> 14:04.093
Because I don't
doubt mine.

14:05.840 --> 14:07.740
All I want to do
is quell this--

14:07.800 --> 14:11.099
this fear
that's taking hold.

14:11.150 --> 14:14.278
You once told me that
you wanted to save lives.

14:14.330 --> 14:16.673
Okay, that's what
this is about.

14:18.240 --> 14:19.844
Don't lose sight
of that.

14:30.040 --> 14:32.861
- Will: So, you were
a driller, huh?
- Holleood: Yep.

14:32.910 --> 14:35.378
