that was the hardest part
for me.

14:42.920 --> 14:44.478
I do miss
that check, though.

14:44.530 --> 14:46.919
Yeah, when those
oil prices fell,

14:46.970 --> 14:48.528
bottom just went out.

14:48.580 --> 14:50.571
- Nobody was safe.
- Company doesn't want

14:50.620 --> 14:53.623
to give up profits,
so people be damned,
you know?

14:53.670 --> 14:55.444
I'm just hoping
for something permanent

14:55.500 --> 14:57.843
before my benefits
run out...

14:57.890 --> 15:01.587
Man:
Mr. Royle, this is
Holleood Desonier,

15:01.630 --> 15:03.939
the man who
got us back on track
these last three weeks.

15:03.990 --> 15:05.241
Hey, I can't take
all the credit.

15:05.290 --> 15:07.850
The whole team
makes it happen.

15:07.900 --> 15:09.891
Well, thanks
for the whole team.

15:09.950 --> 15:12.293
We're gonna miss
our tee time here, John.

15:12.340 --> 15:14.251
You, uh, boys keep up
the good work.

15:14.300 --> 15:16.382
Right this way,
gentlemen.

15:21.000 --> 15:22.911
[ music playing ]

15:27.400 --> 15:30.221
[ gasps ]
That's a beautiful picture.

15:30.270 --> 15:33.831
- It's my family tree.
