16:23.240 --> 16:25.014
Quincy and Darlene.

16:25.070 --> 16:28.801
And when did
they get married?

16:28.850 --> 16:34.595
Let's see, um...
1988, I think.

16:43.820 --> 16:48.257
Blue, we have
something to tell you.

16:48.310 --> 16:49.470
Guess what.

16:51.790 --> 16:54.395
Me and Mama
are getting married.

16:54.440 --> 16:57.182
So, you'll be
together forever?

16:57.230 --> 16:59.312
- Forever.
